Package com.amazon.ion

Interface IonNumber

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, IonValue
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IonDecimal
    public interface IonNumber
extends IonValue
    The IonNumber interface is a fore runner of a common base for the ion numeric value types. Currently only IonDecimal extends this interface. In due course IonFloat and IonInt will be added to the the family.

    WARNING: This interface should not be implemented or extended by code outside of this library.
